[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]We need a clear statement of what it is we are asking schools to deliver. This should then form the basis of how schools are judged and held accountable by Ofsted.[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Strong leadership and governance are key to ensuring successful education outcomes for young people, and Ofsted should continue to focus more acut[bold]ely on this.[bold]&#xa0;
